  "title": "feat(transformData): add transformData to every widget using the Template component",
  "body": "I've transferred the `transformData` call to the `Template` component because it seemed logical to put it here. Does this work for you guys ?\n\nOn widgets with header and footer, `transformData` is only used for item right now. Should we also enable it on header and footer?\n\nFor `hits`, which is the only one with two `Template`s, here is the API:\n\n``` js\ntransformData: {\n  empty: function (data) { /* ... */ },\n  hit: function (data) { /* ... */ }\n}\n```\n",
